7;s the only WordCamp running in the north of England this year. The schedule for the conference day has been announced with topics for the talks including accessibility, SEO, security, managing clients, design and (of course) [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Dave Pullig\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1991:\"<p><a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/wordcamp-manchester-2018.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-998 size-medium\" src=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/wordcamp-manchester-2018-300x148.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Manchester 2018 Logo\" width=\"300\" height=\"148\" srcset=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/wordcamp-manchester-2018-300x148.jpg 300w, https://en-gb.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/wordcamp-manchester-2018-768x378.jpg 768w, https://en-gb.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/wordcamp-manchester-2018-1024x504.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WordCamp Manchester is returning to it&#8217;s regular venue, theManchester Metropolitan Universitys Business School Building on Saturday the 27th October. It&#8217;s the only WordCamp running in the north of England this year.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://2018.manchester.wordcamp.org/schedule/\">schedule for the conference day</a> has been announced with topics for the talks including accessibility, SEO, security, managing clients, design and (of course) the new WordPress editor &#8211; Gutenberg. There will be two tracks on the day, with 7 talks in each along with a lightning talk session per track. Between talks, there will be a chance to network with the other attendees and meet the sponsors in the sponsor area.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2018.manchester.wordcamp.org/tickets/\">Tickets for the conference</a> are priced at 35 which includes refreshments, lunch and an invite to the after party (which will be held at the MMU Students Union building).</p>\n<p>There is also a contributor day being held on Sunday28th October atZiferblat in the Northern Quarter. Tickets to contributor day are also available and are free, again food and lunch are provided. First time contributors are particularly welcome.</p>\n<p>There are also opportunities still available to <a href=\"https://2018.manchester.wordcamp.org/2018/07/30/call-for-sponsors/\">sponsor WordCamp Manchester.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/2018/09/25/wordcamp-manchester-2018-schedule-announced/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Two events in Glasgow this September\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/2018/09/03/two-events-in-glasgow-this-september/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\